    <description>This Record-Triggered Flow is used in the Product Management Tool (PMT) to automatically notify relevant distribution lists based on project status updates.
An email notification is sent when a PMT project is marked as Activated, On Hold, Cancelled.
Each status triggers a specific email template sent to all distribution lists defined at the project level.

ESG (responsible.investment@carmignac.com) is included only if SFDR Category = 6, 8 or 9</description>
